% - Load a broad default stack for assignment/homework workflows.
%
% How to use:
% - Usually do not re-import these packages in your .tex unless you need special
%   options not already enabled here.
%
% Compatibility notes:
% - xcolor is loaded exactly once (historically it was loaded twice).
% - Engine guard keeps pdfLaTeX-friendly encoding setup while staying clean on
%   XeLaTeX/LuaLaTeX.
